die. Turn Left n Route 50, go through Aldie, the church will be on your left.</p>\r\n', 'Directions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '16-autosave', '', '', '2010-09-24 12:08:10', '2010-09-24 12:08:10', '', 16, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch.com/archives/29', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
