(68, 1, '2010-09-22 18:16:53', '2010-09-22 18:16:53', 'There is music and a choir at the 10am service. We choose a wide variety of modern and classical music from <em>The Hymnal 1982, Renew</em>, and<em> Lift Every Voice and Sing</em>.We have enough old Baptists in our congregation to ensure that a wide variety of the classics get sung.\r\n\r\nAdditionally, we present a children''s christmas concert during Advent.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to join the choir, you are invited to show up at practice on Thursday nights at 7:30.', 'What do you do for music?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'what-do-you-do-for-music', '', '', '2010-09-24 15:03:18', '2010-09-24 15:03:18', '', 0, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch.com/?p=68', 0, 'post', '', 0),
