(81, 1, '2010-09-22 18:44:42', '2010-09-22 18:44:42', 'Mostly, you just show up :) We don''t carry badges that say "Episcopal" and "Other."\r\n\r\nBeyond that, if you officially want to be an Episcopalian, you must either be baptised or transfer from another church, and be "received" by the Bishop during his yearly visit. For details, please contact the church at (703)327-4060.', 'How do I join?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'how-do-i-join', '', '', '2010-09-24 15:38:49', '2010-09-24 15:38:49', '', 0, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch.com/?p=81', 0, 'post', '', 0),
