(89, 1, '2010-09-22 18:55:53', '2010-09-22 18:55:53', 'C. Michael Patton comes out of Dallas Theological Seminary, and has a passion for training lay people in how to do theology. Check out "Theology Unplugged," a podcast that will teach you how to "do" theology without necessarily going to seminary, and his blog which I think is pretty well done.\r\n\r\nHere''s the link: <a href="http://www.reclaimingthemind.org/blog/">http://www.reclaimingthemind.org/blog/</a>\r\n\r\nMichael.', 'Parchment & Pen', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'parchment-pen', '', '', '2010-09-23 16:01:02', '2010-09-23 16:01:02', '', 0, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch.com/?p=89', 0, 'post', '', 0),
