(94, 1, '2010-09-22 18:59:03', '2010-09-22 18:59:03', 'Ever wanted to read the ancient church texts? You know, you may have heard of "Macabees" or "The Didache." Basically, if you know that the church didn''t necessarily start in the 20th Century, you owe it to yourself to read the classics. What you don''t owe is some book publisher lots of money to do it.  The <a href="http://www.ccel.org/">Christian Classics Ethereal Library</a> is an easy way to read the old texts.', 'CCEL.org', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'ccel-org', '', '', '2010-09-23 16:01:02', '2010-09-23 16:01:02', '', 0, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch.com/?p=94', 0, 'post', '', 0),
