(144, 1, '2010-09-22 17:49:31', '2010-09-22 17:49:31', '<p>The Church of Our Redeemer is located on Route 50 (John Mosby Highway) in the village of Aldie at <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=39518+John+Mosby+Highway,+Aldie,+VA&amp;sll=38.975075,-77.634737&amp;sspn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=39518+John+Mosby+Hwy,+Aldie,+Loudoun,+Virginia+20105&amp;ll=38.975225,-77.636969&amp;spn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;z=16" mce_href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=39518+John+Mosby+Highway,+Aldie,+VA&amp;sll=38.975075,-77.634737&amp;sspn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=39518+John+Mosby+Hwy,+Aldie,+Loudoun,+Virginia+20105&amp;ll=38.975225,-77.636969&amp;spn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;z=16">39518 John Mosby Highway ·  Aldie, VA 20105</a>. The church is 1 mile west of the traffic circle where Route 15 (north to Leesburg, south to Haymarket) and Route 50 (west to Middleburg, east to South Riding) intersect.&nbsp; For directions, <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=39518+John+Mosby+Highway,+Aldie,+VA&amp;sll=38.975075,-77.634737&amp;sspn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=39518+John+Mosby+Hwy,+Aldie,+Loudoun,+Virginia+20105&amp;ll=38.975225,-77.636969&amp;spn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;z=16" mce_href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=39518+John+Mosby+Highway,+Aldie,+VA&amp;sll=38.975075,-77.634737&amp;sspn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=39518+John+Mosby+Hwy,+Aldie,+Loudoun,+Virginia+20105&amp;ll=38.975225,-77.636969&amp;spn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;z=16">click here</a> or look at the map below.</p><p><br></p><p><a href="http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch.com/directions/directions" rel="attachment wp-att-21"><img src="../wp-content/uploads/2010/09/directions.png" alt="Directions to Church of Our Redeemer" title="directions" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21" width="288" height="144"></a></p>\r\n<p><br></p><p>From South Riding, head west on Route 50, past the three traffic circles. The church will be on your right.<br>\r\nFrom Leesburg, head south on 15, turn right onto Route 50. The church will be on your right.<br>\r\nFrom Haymarket, I-66, and points south, head north on 15, go 3/4 around the traffic circle onto Route 50 west. The church will be on your right.<br>\r\nFrom Middleburg and points west, head east on Route 50, past Snickersville Turnpike, and through Aldie. The church will be on your left.</p>', 'Directions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '16-revision-16', '', '', '2010-09-22 17:49:31', '2010-09-22 17:49:31', '', 16, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch/archives/144', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(145, 1, '2010-09-23 16:48:46', '2010-09-23 16:48:46', '<p>The Church of Our Redeemer is located on Route 50 (John Mosby Highway) in the village of Aldie at <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=39518+John+Mosby+Highway,+Aldie,+VA&amp;sll=38.975075,-77.634737&amp;sspn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=39518+John+Mosby+Hwy,+Aldie,+Loudoun,+Virginia+20105&amp;ll=38.975225,-77.636969&amp;spn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;z=16" mce_href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=39518+John+Mosby+Highway,+Aldie,+VA&amp;sll=38.975075,-77.634737&amp;sspn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=39518+John+Mosby+Hwy,+Aldie,+Loudoun,+Virginia+20105&amp;ll=38.975225,-77.636969&amp;spn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;z=16">39518 John Mosby Highway ·  Aldie, VA 20105</a>. The church is 1 mile west of the traffic circle where Route 15 (north to Leesburg, south to Haymarket) and Route 50 (west to Middleburg, east to South Riding) intersect.&nbsp; For directions, <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=39518+John+Mosby+Highway,+Aldie,+VA&amp;sll=38.975075,-77.634737&amp;sspn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=39518+John+Mosby+Hwy,+Aldie,+Loudoun,+Virginia+20105&amp;ll=38.975225,-77.636969&amp;spn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;z=16" mce_href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=39518+John+Mosby+Highway,+Aldie,+VA&amp;sll=38.975075,-77.634737&amp;sspn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=39518+John+Mosby+Hwy,+Aldie,+Loudoun,+Virginia+20105&amp;ll=38.975225,-77.636969&amp;spn=0.008741,0.022724&amp;z=16">click here</a> or look at the map below.</p><p><br></p><p><a href="http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch.com/directions/directions" rel="attachment wp-att-21"><img src="../wp-content/uploads/2010/09/directions.png" alt="Directions to Church of Our Redeemer" title="directions" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21" width="288" height="144"></a></p>\r\n<p><br></p><p>From South Riding, head west on Route 50, past the three traffic circles. The church will be on your right.<br>\r\nFrom Leesburg, head south on 15, turn right onto Route 50. The church will be on your right.<br>\r\nFrom Haymarket, I-66, and points south, head north on 15, go 3/4 around the traffic circle onto Route 50 west. The church will be on your right.<br>\r\nFrom Middleburg and points west, head east on Route 50, past Snickersville Turnpike, and through Aldie. The church will be on your left.</p>', 'Directions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '16-revision-17', '', '', '2010-09-23 16:48:46', '2010-09-23 16:48:46', '', 16, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch/archives/145', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
