\r\n\r\nFrom <strong>Purcellville</strong>, take S. 20th Street (611 / Telegraph Springs Road / New Ford Road) to Snickersville Turnpike. Turn Right on Snickersville Turnpike (734). Continue on 734 until it ends in Aldie. Turn Left n Route 50, go through Aldie, the church will be on your left.', 'Directions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '16-revision-25', '', '', '2010-09-24 11:07:32', '2010-09-24 11:07:32', '', 16, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch/archives/193', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
