e 50, go through Aldie, the church will be on your left.</p>\r\n', 'Directions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '16-revision-32', '', '', '2010-09-24 12:06:20', '2010-09-24 12:06:20', '', 16, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch/archives/200', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
