out with her coming!'' " 6 And the Lord said, "Listen to what the unjust judge says. 7 And will not God bring about justice for his chosen ones, who cry out to him day and night? Will he keep putting them off? 8 I tell you, he will see that they get justice, and quickly. However, when the Son of Man comes, will he find faith on the earth?"', '', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '271-revision-2', '', '', '2010-10-25 13:21:12', '2010-10-25 18:21:12', '', 271, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch/archives/273', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
