(275, 1, '2010-10-25 14:25:24', '2010-10-25 19:25:24', 'Does your Christmas list cross international boundaries? Well, if  God''s love is no respecter of borders, neither should your Christmas  list!  This year, millions of children from around the globe need  everything from toys to toothbrushes, and you can be a part of that.\r\n\r\nIf you will simply purchase a few toys and hygenic items, place them  in a shoebox, or a shoebox-sized plastic container, wrap a rubber band  around it, and bring it to the church before November 21st, we will make  sure that you bring Christmas to a child in need.\r\n\r\nFor more details, check out <a href="http://www.samaritanspurse.org/index.php/OCC/" target="_blank">http://www.samaritanspurse.org/index.php/OCC/</a> or contact Laura Tekrony (at our church!) for details.', 'Operation Christmas Child – Nov 21st.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'operation-christmas-child-nov-21st', '', '', '2010-10-25 14:26:09', '2010-10-25 19:26:09', '', 0, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch/?p=275', 0, 'post', '', 0),
