(277, 1, '2010-09-24 18:17:20', '2010-09-24 18:17:20', 'Back by popular acclaim, GateWay, the teen-led, teen-fed service for 7th through 12th Graders at Church of Our Redeemer will be starting soon. We meet on the 1st &amp; 3rd Sundays of each month during the main 10am service in the room at the end of the hall.  See you there!', 'GateWay is Starting October 3rd!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '227-revision-2', '', '', '2010-09-24 18:17:20', '2010-09-24 18:17:20', '', 227, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch/archives/277', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
